- content_for :page_title
  ' ColourVariant Index:

.panel.panel-danger
  .panel-heading
    ' BIG RED BUTTON
  .panel-body
    p If you don't know what this does, don't touch it.
    p This will cause performance degradation while things are rebuilt.

    ul
      li Wipes and reindexes colour variants
      li Wipes and reindexes products
      li Clears Cache
      li Clears Product Discount Repository
      li Clears Taxon Repository

    p All actions are logged.

    = form_tag( {controller: :product_indexes, action: :clear}, {method: :delete, class: 'form-inline'}) do
      .form-group
        label
        = text_field_tag :really_really, nil, placeholder: 'Type REALLY', class: 'form-control', required: true
      .form-group
        button.btn.btn-danger BIG RED BUTTON

table.table.admin-table-condensed
  thead : tr
    th id
    th product_id
    th product_name
    th sku
    th color
  tbody
    - @search.results.each do |res|
      tr
       td
         = link_to res.id, {controller: :product_indexes, action: :show, id: res.id }
       td = res.product.id
       td = res.product.name
       td = res.product.sku
       td = res.color.try(:presentation)

